fields.name: ABS
fields.description: Acrylonitrile Butadiene Styrene (ABS) is often used for telephone handsets, cars, shower trays, rigid luggage, domestic appliance housings (food mixers), electroplated parts, radiator grills, handles, computer housings.

fields.name: HDPE
fields.description: High Density Polyethylene (HDPE) is a popular packaging choice for the milk and fresh juice industry as well as pipes, chemical cans, crates, packaging, pallets, wheelie bins, bags, profiles and more.

fields.name: LDPE
fields.description: Low Density Polyethylene (LDPE) used for shrink wrap, films, carrier bags, caps, general packaging and water pipes.

fields.name: MDPE
fields.description: Medium Density Polyethylene (MDPE), used for kayaks, water tanks, drums & pipes

fields.name: PET
fields.description: Polyethylene Terephthalate (PT), widely used for drinks bottles, trays, polyester fibre, films and strapping.

fields.name: PVC
fields.description: Polyvinyl Chloride (PVC), used for window frames, credit cards, pipes, profiles, trays, faux leather, binder covers and door skins.

fields.name: Other
fields.description: We can deal with other specialist plastic such as PE/PA, TPE, TPO, PC/ABS, PE100 and more.
